data.title: QuickTree
data.description: an efficient implementation of the Neighbor-Joining algorithm.

evidence: "QuickTree is an efficient implementation of the Neighbor-Joining algorithm ... capable of reconstructing phylogenies from huge alignments"

"QuickTree is written in ANSI C and should complile and run on a number of different platforms. 'make quicktree' from this directory should compile the program and place the executable in the current directory."
"Any problems, please contact klh@ebi.ac.uk / Kevin Howe, 2002"
